The Kupocard Mini Returns!

Until Wed., Mar. 27, 07:59 UTC

The Kupocard Mini is back!

The Kupocard Mini will give you 800 Initial Gems and seven days of 100 Daily Gems － that's a total of 1,500 Gems!

If you purchase the Kupocard Mini four times (maximum) during the campaign, you can receive a grand total of 6,000 Gems!

It will be here until Wed., Mar. 27, at 07:59 UTC, so don't miss out!

About the Kupocard Mini

Kupocard Mini

  • Initial Gems: 800
  • Daily Gems: 100 (for 7 days)
  • Total Gems: 1,500

Upon purchase, you will receive the Initial Gems immediately, and the Daily Gems will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your Daily Bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh Daily Gems reward, you can purchase another Kupocard Mini as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can get up to four during this period!

You can purchase the Kupocard Mini 2 alongside the Kupocard Mini.

* Logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
